author: Charles Dickens
message: Don't leave a stone unturned. It's always something, to know you have done the most you could.
title: Thought of the day

author: Dalai Lama
message: By going beyond your own problems and taking care of others, you gain inner strength, self-confidence, courage, and a greater sense of calm.
title: Thought of the day

author: Sam Keen
message: We come to love not by finding a perfect person, but by learning to see an imperfect person perfectly.
title: Thought of the day

author: Walt Emerson
message: What lies behind us and what lies before us are tiny matters compared to what lies within us.
title: Thought of the day
